{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d6a1d88142","title":"对创办三所军医大学报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b6e5449b5","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":14,"articleId":"d6a1d88142"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"7babadc490","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会总后方勤务部卫生部部长贺诚和副部长傅连障1949年11月12日报告的批语。"},{"id":"b08debcd68","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"贺诚和傅连障的报告提议创办3所军医大学：一、将华北医科大学（又名白求恩医科大学）改为军医大学，主要轮训团级以上干部。二、拟将上海伪国防医学院，改为上海军医大学，轮训团级以下卫生干部及招收新生培训。三、将东北之长春医科大学改为长春军医大学，训练海空军卫生干部与轮训团级以下卫生干部。"},{"id":"1fe2567586","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指贺诚报告中所提出的华北医科大学迁址建议。报告认为，该校现在石家庄，占用民房，群众意见甚多，应迁到北京或天津。其中第二项办法为迁至天津，与河北医学院合并，改为军医大学。"}],"contents":[{"id":"26e4b0a8c1","type":"title","text":"对创办三所军医大学报告的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142"},{"id":"7babadc490","type":"subtitle","text":"照办。以","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142"},{"id":"b08debcd68","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142"},{"id":"1fe2567586","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十四日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142"},{"id":"2cdcc341e2","type":"subtitle","text":"第一问题两项似以第二项办法较妥。以","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142"}],"page":{"id":"655b0062d4","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"d6a1d88142","start":516,"end":516}}}},"__N_SSG":true}